{"tid":2063494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國瑜支持者舉行集會 有代表台上稱要「槍斃蔡英文」或違法","createTime":"2020-06-14T05:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T05:27:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d122e7257c23d881d8996a1bbb034606531a8b35","tid":2063494,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「民主監督聯盟」召集人黃正忠今（13）日舉辦「百萬白衫軍 庶民上凱道」遊行活動，但不僅現場人數一度比警方還少，連知名韓粉直播主高鈞鈞到場也傻眼，「現場人是真的不多」。未料退休台北城市科大教授周明台代表上台發言時，竟率眾高喊「罷掉蔡英文！槍斃蔡英文！」而此舉恐已觸犯刑法《恐嚇危害安全罪》。<br />\n<br />\n民主監督聯盟今下午在凱道舉辦活動，依主辦單位向警方申請流程，活動從下午2點30分開始，晚間10時結束。綜合媒體報導，活動現場還開放民眾登記發言，沒想到退休教授周明台上台時，公開表示要大家勇敢站出來替天行道，為已故高市議長許崑源討公道，甚至還呼籲大家團結把總統蔡英文拉下來，「罷免蔡英文！槍斃蔡英文！」<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3196879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196879&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=d1152c18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196879&h=0a29ad1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3196879</a>"},{"pid":"519df05abfc45c498ed502b7fbcadac0ff7a6508","tid":2063494,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a046fe4dc760a4b6161f003b2ad6f454173665e","tid":2063494,"uid":69,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d122e7257c23d881d8996a1bbb034606531a8b35","tid":2063494,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「民主監督聯盟」召集人黃正忠今（13）日舉辦「百萬白衫軍 庶民上凱道」遊行活動，但不僅現場人數一度比警方還少，連知名韓粉直播主高鈞鈞到場也傻眼，「現場人是真的不多」。未料退休台北城市科大教授周明台代表上台發言時，竟率眾高喊「罷掉蔡英文！槍斃蔡英文！」而此舉恐已觸犯刑法《恐嚇危害安全罪》。<br />\n<br />\n民主監督聯盟今下午在凱道舉辦活動，依主辦單位向警方申請流程，活動從下午2點30分開始，晚間10時結束。綜合媒體報導，活動現場還開放民眾登記發言，沒想到退休教授周明台上台時，公開表示要大家勇敢站出來替天行道，為已故高市議長許崑源討公道，甚至還呼籲大家團結把總統蔡英文拉下來，「罷免蔡英文！槍斃蔡英文！」<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3196879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196879&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=d1152c18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196879&h=0a29ad1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3196879</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"藍絲真係有樣睇"},{"pid":"3ecf982b82c656280bdbb3790febd793a8e67249","tid":2063494,"uid":61325,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"殺無赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d28ac9ae3feb69e03c0de21eff734886f4f74c1","tid":2063494,"uid":74361,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"如果蔡英文死左,大家知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1be8e731dc776c65772d76db68e35cf5e1f9f6b","tid":2063494,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"一千人都唔夠"},{"pid":"9a00b9052ddd280a7bc497978b6b45cd29d539ab","tid":2063494,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"對此，台北市警察局中正一分局表示，針對相關言論，會在活動結束後，透過現場蒐證畫面了解當事人言論，若涉及違法，會依法傳喚當事人說明。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，此言論恐涉及刑法恐嚇危害安全罪或恐嚇公眾罪，但仍須依現場蒐證影片及傳喚當事人說明後，才能依法究辦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/asoc/202006130171.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faso